Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最终能遵守约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是 自己会打破约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都取决于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九话 在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 带大家出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你为什么这么愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们被杀害 怎么可能不生气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我回去 我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别挡着 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明约好了要保护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 直接叫你名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮岛神社神主 更衣唯芳的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三荆学园的二年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣小夜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈子 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些 都是你杀的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护 学校的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 宁宁还有优花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没做 只是呆在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是负责思考的头脑 还是负责感受的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是心?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天发生了重大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该离结束不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和谁做的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一下 回答刚才的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为什么每当要得到答案的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被什么东西阻塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了班长 连优花同学也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学今天在学校?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后知道怪物来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天学校有通知要上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所有人都通知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复课的消息应该所有人都通知到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么学校中除了B班没有别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校中一边和古物战斗一边跑啊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 谁都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只看到了筒鸟老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的老师都去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为 担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢? 我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在同一个班上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有喜欢的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你在一起有多长时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班的时真慎一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这种时候外出很危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为话还没有说完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是 更衣小夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是更衣小夜 高中二年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任是筒鸟老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友有宁宁 诺诺 优花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也和班长 时真同学说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是更衣唯芳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浮岛神社的神主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道母亲的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道母亲的名字和面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是更衣小夜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLooD-C 下一话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜之秋


